AMERICAN LIBERTY OIL COMPANY, Appellant, v. HUNT COUNTY, Texas, Appellee. No. 12465. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. March 17, 1949. Russell Allen, W. B. Harrell and C. C. Renfro, all of Dallas, Tex., for appellant. Harold B. Sanders, of Dallas, Tex., and Allen Clark and A. S. Rollins, both of Greenville, Tex., for appellee.

Before HUTCHESON, HOLMES, and LEE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

,The Judgment appealed from is affirmed.
